skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: kates chores
des: Happy life, happy life. This skill will give you a list of chores and when asked, will tell you what needs to be done in and around the house. Never forget a single chore and keep Kate happy. Just ask Alexa what Kate wants and she's sure to let you know.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
